 I have already started the sPHENIX singularity container.
 Run the setup script and you are in business.
 
 # source /opt/sphenix/core/bin/sphenix_setup.sh -n

 The core-software respository for sPHENIX collaboration is

 # https://github.com/sPHENIX-Collaboration/coresoftware

 Official macros and tutorials can be obtained from

 # git clone https://github.com/sPHENIX-Collaboration/macros.git
 # git clone https://github.com/sPHENIX-Collaboration/tutorials.git

